### 5. **State Management Patterns**

**Local State:**
```jsx
const [formData, setFormData] = useState({
    name: '',
    email: '',
    age: 0
});

const handleInputChange = (field) => (event) => {
    setFormData(prev => ({
        ...prev,
        [field]: event.target.value
